    "以下のテキストを普段どおりの声で読み上げてください。録音後に自動で声紋を登録します。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Please read the following text in your normal voice. Your voiceprint will be registered automatically after recording."
          }
        }
