    },
    "「今日はとてもいい天気ですね。こんな日は散歩にでも出かけたくなります。最近は忙しくてなかなか外に出られないけれど、たまにはゆっくり過ごしたいものです。」": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"It's such a beautiful day today. On days like this, I feel like going for a walk. I've been busy lately and haven't been able to get outside much, but I'd like to take it easy once in a while.\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
